### Common Mistakes (Don't run these, just for reference)

# 1. Trailing Comma (Invalid)
# {
#   "email": "test@test.com",
#   "password": "123",  <-- Error here
# }

# 2. Single Quotes (Invalid)
# {
#   'email': 'test@test.com' <-- JSON requires double quotes "
# }

# 3. Missing Quotes on Keys (Invalid)
# {
#   email: "test@test.com" <-- Keys must be quoted "email"
# }
